{"code":"DX-CARD-5F28B989F353","id":"DX-CARD-5F28B989F353","entityType":"DiagnosisCriteria","name":"心电图传导阻滞诊断依据","component_status":"component_refined","component_count_after_batch":8,"knowledge_layer":"textbook_skeleton","source_type":"authoritative_textbook","batch_id":"BATCH-CARD-DXC-AVB-COMP-20260714-001","schema_version":"V1.12","clinical_use_status":"knowledge_display_with_components","formal_cdss_ready":false,"clinical_review_status":"review_ready","review_status":"review_ready","updated_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","governance_note":"共享传导阻滞诊断标准已补充房室传导阻滞、窦房传导阻滞和缓慢性心律失常的可下钻诊断明细。"}
{"code":"DXCOMP-CARD-AVB-GENERAL-20260714","id":"DXCOMP-CARD-AVB-GENERAL-20260714","entityType":"DiagnosisCriteriaComponent","name":"房室传导阻滞总体诊断依据","standard_name":"房室传导阻滞总体诊断依据","中文类型":"诊断标准明细","definition":"房室传导阻滞是房室交界区脱离生理不应期后，心房冲动传导延迟或不能传导至心室；按严重程度分为一度、二度和三度。","component_text":"房室传导阻滞是房室交界区脱离生理不应期后，心房冲动传导延迟或不能传导至心室；按严重程度分为一度、二度和三度。","structured_logic":"房室传导延迟或中断；按传导受阻程度分型。","component_role":"diagnostic_basis","component_kind":"definition_and_classification","parent_criteria_code":"DX-CARD-5F28B989F353","parent_criteria_name":"心电图传导阻滞诊断依据","source_evidence_code":"EVD-16A802061D09515EA9E8-AVB","source_name":"《内科学（第10版）》","source_type":"authoritative_textbook","source_page":"245","knowledge_layer":"textbook_skeleton","skeleton_slot":"diagnosis_and_differential_diagnosis","applicable_disease_codes":["DIS-CARD-ARR-AVB","DIS-CARD-ARR-AVB1","DIS-CARD-ARR-AVB2","DIS-CARD-ARR-AVB3"],"sort_order":10,"batch_id":"BATCH-CARD-DXC-AVB-COMP-20260714-001","schema_version":"V1.12","clinical_use_status":"knowledge_display_only","formal_cdss_ready":false,"clinical_review_status":"review_ready","review_status":"review_ready","quality_gate":"G2_import_ready","created_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","updated_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","governance_note":"教材骨架诊断标准明细补齐；用于前端下钻展示和后续规则结构化，不直接作为自动处方推荐。"}
{"code":"DXCOMP-CARD-AVB1-PR-20260714","id":"DXCOMP-CARD-AVB1-PR-20260714","entityType":"DiagnosisCriteriaComponent","name":"一度房室传导阻滞心电图标准","standard_name":"一度房室传导阻滞心电图标准","中文类型":"诊断标准明细","definition":"PR间期超过0.20秒，QRS波群形态与时限正常。","component_text":"PR间期超过0.20秒，QRS波群形态与时限正常。","structured_logic":"PR间期>0.20秒且每个心房冲动仍能下传。","component_role":"ecg_criterion","component_kind":"threshold_rule","parent_criteria_code":"DX-CARD-5F28B989F353","parent_criteria_name":"心电图传导阻滞诊断依据","source_evidence_code":"EVD-1B1E62A8472E1475EFC1-AVB1","source_name":"《内科学（第10版）》","source_type":"authoritative_textbook","source_page":"N/A","knowledge_layer":"textbook_skeleton","skeleton_slot":"diagnosis_and_differential_diagnosis","applicable_disease_codes":["DIS-CARD-ARR-AVB1","DIS-CARD-ARR-AVB"],"sort_order":20,"batch_id":"BATCH-CARD-DXC-AVB-COMP-20260714-001","schema_version":"V1.12","clinical_use_status":"knowledge_display_only","formal_cdss_ready":false,"clinical_review_status":"review_ready","review_status":"review_ready","quality_gate":"G2_import_ready","created_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","updated_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","governance_note":"教材骨架诊断标准明细补齐；用于前端下钻展示和后续规则结构化，不直接作为自动处方推荐。","threshold_value":"PR间期>0.20秒"}
{"code":"DXCOMP-CARD-AVB2-MOBITZ-I-20260714","id":"DXCOMP-CARD-AVB2-MOBITZ-I-20260714","entityType":"DiagnosisCriteriaComponent","name":"二度Ⅰ型房室传导阻滞心电图标准","standard_name":"二度Ⅰ型房室传导阻滞心电图标准","中文类型":"诊断标准明细","definition":"P波规律出现，PR间期逐渐延长，直到P波下传受阻，脱漏1个QRS波群；常见房室传导比例为3∶2和5∶4。","component_text":"P波规律出现，PR间期逐渐延长，直到P波下传受阻，脱漏1个QRS波群；常见房室传导比例为3∶2和5∶4。","structured_logic":"P波规律；PR逐渐延长；随后出现一次QRS脱漏。","component_role":"ecg_criterion","component_kind":"pattern_rule","parent_criteria_code":"DX-CARD-5F28B989F353","parent_criteria_name":"心电图传导阻滞诊断依据","source_evidence_code":"EVD-B1283A597FF38E5672DA-AVB","source_name":"《内科学（第10版）》","source_type":"authoritative_textbook","source_page":"245","knowledge_layer":"textbook_skeleton","skeleton_slot":"diagnosis_and_differential_diagnosis","applicable_disease_codes":["DIS-CARD-ARR-AVB2","DIS-CARD-ARR-AVB"],"sort_order":30,"batch_id":"BATCH-CARD-DXC-AVB-COMP-20260714-001","schema_version":"V1.12","clinical_use_status":"knowledge_display_only","formal_cdss_ready":false,"clinical_review_status":"review_ready","review_status":"review_ready","quality_gate":"G2_import_ready","created_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","updated_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","governance_note":"教材骨架诊断标准明细补齐；用于前端下钻展示和后续规则结构化，不直接作为自动处方推荐。"}
{"code":"DXCOMP-CARD-AVB2-MOBITZ-II-20260714","id":"DXCOMP-CARD-AVB2-MOBITZ-II-20260714","entityType":"DiagnosisCriteriaComponent","name":"二度Ⅱ型房室传导阻滞心电图标准","standard_name":"二度Ⅱ型房室传导阻滞心电图标准","中文类型":"诊断标准明细","definition":"PR间期恒定，部分P波后无QRS波群；QRS波群增宽且形态异常时，阻滞多位于希氏束-浦肯野纤维系统。","component_text":"PR间期恒定，部分P波后无QRS波群；QRS波群增宽且形态异常时，阻滞多位于希氏束-浦肯野纤维系统。","structured_logic":"PR恒定；部分P波不能下传；可伴QRS增宽。","component_role":"ecg_criterion","component_kind":"pattern_rule","parent_criteria_code":"DX-CARD-5F28B989F353","parent_criteria_name":"心电图传导阻滞诊断依据","source_evidence_code":"EVD-F5F0A207C51A014082F4-AVB","source_name":"《内科学（第10版）》","source_type":"authoritative_textbook","source_page":"246","knowledge_layer":"textbook_skeleton","skeleton_slot":"diagnosis_and_differential_diagnosis","applicable_disease_codes":["DIS-CARD-ARR-AVB2","DIS-CARD-ARR-AVB"],"sort_order":40,"batch_id":"BATCH-CARD-DXC-AVB-COMP-20260714-001","schema_version":"V1.12","clinical_use_status":"knowledge_display_only","formal_cdss_ready":false,"clinical_review_status":"review_ready","review_status":"review_ready","quality_gate":"G2_import_ready","created_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","updated_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","governance_note":"教材骨架诊断标准明细补齐；用于前端下钻展示和后续规则结构化，不直接作为自动处方推荐。"}
{"code":"DXCOMP-CARD-AVB-HIGH-GRADE-20260714","id":"DXCOMP-CARD-AVB-HIGH-GRADE-20260714","entityType":"DiagnosisCriteriaComponent","name":"高度房室传导阻滞心电图标准","standard_name":"高度房室传导阻滞心电图标准","中文类型":"诊断标准明细","definition":"连续两个或两个以上P波不能下传心室，通常房室间呈2∶1或3∶1传导。","component_text":"连续两个或两个以上P波不能下传心室，通常房室间呈2∶1或3∶1传导。","structured_logic":"连续≥2个P波未下传；常见2:1或3:1房室传导。","component_role":"ecg_criterion","component_kind":"pattern_rule","parent_criteria_code":"DX-CARD-5F28B989F353","parent_criteria_name":"心电图传导阻滞诊断依据","source_evidence_code":"EVD-CA1E4ED0F67E96B40A15-AVB","source_name":"《内科学（第10版）》","source_type":"authoritative_textbook","source_page":"246","knowledge_layer":"textbook_skeleton","skeleton_slot":"diagnosis_and_differential_diagnosis","applicable_disease_codes":["DIS-CARD-ARR-AVB2","DIS-CARD-ARR-AVB"],"sort_order":50,"batch_id":"BATCH-CARD-DXC-AVB-COMP-20260714-001","schema_version":"V1.12","clinical_use_status":"knowledge_display_only","formal_cdss_ready":false,"clinical_review_status":"review_ready","review_status":"review_ready","quality_gate":"G2_import_ready","created_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","updated_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","governance_note":"教材骨架诊断标准明细补齐；用于前端下钻展示和后续规则结构化，不直接作为自动处方推荐。"}
{"code":"DXCOMP-CARD-AVB3-COMPLETE-20260714","id":"DXCOMP-CARD-AVB3-COMPLETE-20260714","entityType":"DiagnosisCriteriaComponent","name":"三度/完全性房室传导阻滞诊断标准","standard_name":"三度/完全性房室传导阻滞诊断标准","中文类型":"诊断标准明细","definition":"全部心房冲动不能传导至心室，心房和心室节律由各自独立起搏点控制，表现为房室分离。","component_text":"全部心房冲动不能传导至心室，心房和心室节律由各自独立起搏点控制，表现为房室分离。","structured_logic":"心房冲动完全不能下传；心房率与心室率互不相关。","component_role":"ecg_criterion","component_kind":"pattern_rule","parent_criteria_code":"DX-CARD-5F28B989F353","parent_criteria_name":"心电图传导阻滞诊断依据","source_evidence_code":"EVD-16A802061D09515EA9E8-AVB3","source_name":"《内科学（第10版）》","source_type":"authoritative_textbook","source_page":"245","knowledge_layer":"textbook_skeleton","skeleton_slot":"diagnosis_and_differential_diagnosis","applicable_disease_codes":["DIS-CARD-ARR-AVB3","DIS-CARD-ARR-AVB"],"sort_order":60,"batch_id":"BATCH-CARD-DXC-AVB-COMP-20260714-001","schema_version":"V1.12","clinical_use_status":"knowledge_display_only","formal_cdss_ready":false,"clinical_review_status":"review_ready","review_status":"review_ready","quality_gate":"G2_import_ready","created_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","updated_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","governance_note":"教材骨架诊断标准明细补齐；用于前端下钻展示和后续规则结构化，不直接作为自动处方推荐。"}
{"code":"DXCOMP-CARD-SAB-ECG-20260714","id":"DXCOMP-CARD-SAB-ECG-20260714","entityType":"DiagnosisCriteriaComponent","name":"窦房传导阻滞心电图诊断线索","standard_name":"窦房传导阻滞心电图诊断线索","中文类型":"诊断标准明细","definition":"心电图可见窦性停搏、窦性静止或窦房传导阻滞，也可见窦房传导阻滞与房室传导阻滞并存。","component_text":"心电图可见窦性停搏、窦性静止或窦房传导阻滞，也可见窦房传导阻滞与房室传导阻滞并存。","structured_logic":"疑似窦房结功能障碍时，结合窦性停搏/窦房传导阻滞表现及症状-心电图相关性判断。","component_role":"ecg_criterion","component_kind":"pattern_rule","parent_criteria_code":"DX-CARD-5F28B989F353","parent_criteria_name":"心电图传导阻滞诊断依据","source_evidence_code":"EVD-03738107C48965887852-SAB","source_name":"《内科学（第10版）》","source_type":"authoritative_textbook","source_page":"228","knowledge_layer":"textbook_skeleton","skeleton_slot":"diagnosis_and_differential_diagnosis","applicable_disease_codes":["DIS-CARD-ARR-SAB","DIS-CARD-ARR-BRADY"],"sort_order":70,"batch_id":"BATCH-CARD-DXC-AVB-COMP-20260714-001","schema_version":"V1.12","clinical_use_status":"knowledge_display_only","formal_cdss_ready":false,"clinical_review_status":"review_ready","review_status":"review_ready","quality_gate":"G2_import_ready","created_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","updated_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","governance_note":"教材骨架诊断标准明细补齐；用于前端下钻展示和后续规则结构化，不直接作为自动处方推荐。"}
{"code":"DXCOMP-CARD-BRADY-ECG-CORRELATION-20260714","id":"DXCOMP-CARD-BRADY-ECG-CORRELATION-20260714","entityType":"DiagnosisCriteriaComponent","name":"缓慢性心律失常症状-心电图相关性诊断依据","standard_name":"缓慢性心律失常症状-心电图相关性诊断依据","中文类型":"诊断标准明细","definition":"根据心电图典型表现，或临床症状与心电图改变存在明确相关性，可确定相关缓慢性心律失常诊断。","component_text":"根据心电图典型表现，或临床症状与心电图改变存在明确相关性，可确定相关缓慢性心律失常诊断。","structured_logic":"症状与显著心动过缓、心脏停搏或传导阻滞的心电图记录一致时支持诊断。","component_role":"diagnostic_basis","component_kind":"clinical_ecg_correlation","parent_criteria_code":"DX-CARD-5F28B989F353","parent_criteria_name":"心电图传导阻滞诊断依据","source_evidence_code":"EVD-03738107C48965887852-BRADY","source_name":"《内科学（第10版）》","source_type":"authoritative_textbook","source_page":"228","knowledge_layer":"textbook_skeleton","skeleton_slot":"diagnosis_and_differential_diagnosis","applicable_disease_codes":["DIS-CARD-ARR-BRADY","DIS-CARD-ARR-SAB"],"sort_order":80,"batch_id":"BATCH-CARD-DXC-AVB-COMP-20260714-001","schema_version":"V1.12","clinical_use_status":"knowledge_display_only","formal_cdss_ready":false,"clinical_review_status":"review_ready","review_status":"review_ready","quality_gate":"G2_import_ready","created_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","updated_at":"2026-07-14 07:52:17","governance_note":"教材骨架诊断标准明细补齐；用于前端下钻展示和后续规则结构化，不直接作为自动处方推荐。"}
